{"tid":2402088,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【親中BLM】獲拜登政府祝福兼南韓對手退選 尼日利亞前女財長篤定出任新總幹事","createTime":"2021-02-10T08:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T08:31:47.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f188f4a6900dcf7d299de7f4c7c1583a02613af7","tid":2402088,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:03:05.000Z","msg":"美國拜登政府再一次扭轉前朝特朗普政府的決定，周五表態「強烈支持」尼日利亞前財長伊韋阿拉（Ngozi Okonjo-Iweala）出任世界貿易組織(WTO)新任總幹事。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表辦事處在聲明中，形容伊韋阿拉「富經濟與國際外交知識」，而且有管理大型國際組織的經驗。伊韋阿拉雖然獲得不少國家支持，去年10月亦獲世貿遴選委員會推薦出任世貿總幹事，但特朗普卻一直反對，令此職位一直懸空。由於世貿所有決定都需要164個成員國按共識達成，因此美國反對等同否決任命。<br />\n<br />\n在美國表態支持伊韋阿拉的同一天，她的主要競爭對手南韓貿易部長俞明希(Yoo Myung-hee)宣佈退出競逐。兩項新發展令纏繞世貿多月的人事風波趨向明朗。<br />\n<br />\n伊韋阿拉表示期望完成遴選工作，為世貿推動必須的改革。美國貿易代表辦事處說，已準備與伊韋阿拉一起工作，「拜登政府期望與世貿新任總幹事一起工作，以找尋達致推動世貿進行大規模和程序改革的路徑」。<br />\n<br />\n伊韋阿拉的任命若獲確認，將成為世貿25年來首位女性和非裔總幹事。她自2019年成為美國公民，不過美國前貿易代表萊特希澤(Robert Lighthizer)認為伊韋阿拉太接近親貿易國際主義者，如世界銀行前行長羅拔佐利克（Robert Zoellick）。特朗普曾多次抨擊世貿成為全球主義者的工具，讓中國經濟在毫無制約下冒起。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/O_a1fIw3BAm_DRqVfQXzC9K5gqs=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJMQVEROJJAIFJ4L64YEGPIMAQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FO_a1fIw3BAm_DRqVfQXzC9K5gqs%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJMQVEROJJAIFJ4L64YEGPIMAQ.jpg&h=3120b8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image.cache.storm.mg/styles/smg-800x533-fp/s3/media/image/2020/09/07/20200907-073717_U7213_M637277_752f.jpg?itok=xYvDsh4D\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.cache.storm.mg%2Fstyles%2Fsmg-800x533-fp%2Fs3%2Fmedia%2Fimage%2F2020%2F09%2F07%2F20200907-073717_U7213_M637277_752f.jpg%3Fitok%3DxYvDsh4D&h=8f9ac2ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"14a5b00c9d9e844067c60d3c7443c4bb86261d67","tid":2402088,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"黑人+女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adf6864a763a288c1d98b4e1ab6240f2975a3226","tid":2402088,"uid":256837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"wto who兩個都淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ff5098c20dba951878dbf887ea79c480444b3c8","tid":2402088,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:05:28.000Z","msg":"尼日利亞出身帶領各國 維持國際貿易秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2186bbad2e1aa78e882d3ccb14ea71611575d3bb","tid":2402088,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adf6864a763a288c1d98b4e1ab6240f2975a3226","tid":2402088,"uid":256837,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"wto who兩個都淪陷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:05:57.000Z","msg":"聯合國整體都垃撚圾黎"},{"pid":"7a1dee38f70caee5dc9ab464e409562951f57295","tid":2402088,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14a5b00c9d9e844067c60d3c7443c4bb86261d67","tid":2402088,"uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"黑人+女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:06:05.000Z","msg":"Trans呢？"},{"pid":"6a72fa691ae2eef650e6cc57ed44f3bb60b99841","tid":2402088,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:06:34.000Z","msg":"下一個譚德塞？"},{"pid":"d69eaed82499b06638a5a9e432cb09915770d39a","tid":2402088,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4ff5098c20dba951878dbf887ea79c480444b3c8","tid":2402088,"uid":79562,"like":1,"dislike":0,